    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and peak volumetric efficiency. Power is channeled through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the chassis utilizes refreshed bushings for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline offer a visceral, analog performance profile.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
