      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a premium driving experience. The exterior retains a deep, glossy metallic finish, showing only the minor road wear expected from careful daily use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is exceptionally clean, featuring supple leather seating, a panoramic sunroof, and an upgraded sound system. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust; it has a documented service history, a smooth-shifting automatic transmission, and recently replaced tires that provide a quiet, confident ride. All electronics and safety features are fully operational, making this a turn-key option for anyone seeking luxury and dependability at a sensible price point.",
